Viyafikile lulu imwe ya bei ng'hulu, kahita kachuuza vose viyakalile navo na kagula lulu ija."
Chilo chino na weye mukale hano ichilo chino fana viwatendile wawo, mbali niye nizawona yondayanilongele Mndewa Mulungu."
